g.text: Something light or dark? Hoppy or malty? An ale? Lager? Stout? And what is this brand all about?
WE GET IT. YOU WANT THE RIGHT BEER FOR YOU!
Simply take a photo of a beer you’re considering.
All of our info comes directly from breweries themselves, so you know you’re getting the most accurate details available.

There’s never been a better time to get into craft beer. With more and more craft breweries popping up, there’s no shortage of great local beer, and cool brands. But when a new beer catches your eye, how do you know what you’re getting into?
Craft Hero is currently only serving the Calgary area, but we’re expanding rapidly and coming to taprooms and liquor stores near you. Get notified when we launch in your area.
From there we’ll build a flavour profile for you and provide personalized recommendations. Each recommendation comes with a personalized score based on what you’ve liked in the past.

I consent to receiving launch notification emails from Craft Hero. We will not share your personal information with any other organizations or individuals. We do not sell, communicate or divulge your information to any third-parties or mailing lists.

Get more out of your beer list by adding it to Craft Hero. Engage with your customers, provide curated tasting notes, and gain insights into customer preferences and market demand. Enter your information below to connect with someone from the Craft Hero team.
Craft Hero is a full mobile app that acts as your guide to new beer. Using image recognition and personalized flavour profiling, Craft Hero will help you find the beer we know you’ll love.
FIND THE RIGHT BEER WITH CRAFT HERO
